                        <li><a href="#bank-comparison" class="sidebar-link text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600"><i class="fas fa-university mr-2 w-5 text-purple-500"></i>3. Bank Comparison</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#documents" class="sidebar-link text-gray-700 hover:text-blue-600"><i class="fas fa-file-alt mr-2 w-5 text-orange-500"></i>4. Documents Required</a></li>
