                                <li class="checklist-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Bank Statements (6 months)</li>
                                <li class="checklist-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Form 16</li>
